PDA_CMN_20070115.0045	0	30030.000	30039.900				Another public-spirited decision that attracted wide attention was that railway ticket price for passenger transport during the Spring Festival will not be increased starting 2007.	0	0	0		
PDA_CMN_20070115.0045	0	40010.000	40019.900				As we can see, the central government does not turn a blind eye to the over-protection of high prices and failure to perform public duties to their best by some monopolized industries but exerts itself to adopt regulatory measures instead.	0	0	0		
