PDA_CMN_20070115.0045	0	40030.000	40039.900				On the one hand, major spheres such as resources and transportation have public service properties, thus they should maintain relatively stable prices. On the other hand, in order to increase the service efficiency of these spheres, certain market mechanisms should also be implemented in their operations to encourage appropriate competitions.	0	0	0		
PDA_CMN_20070115.0045	0	40040.000	40049.900				I believe that the so-called 'relative integration of market operation and public service functions' should be the integration of market economy and public morals, as well as the integration of economic operational efficiency and the purpose to serve people.	0	0	0		
